Organization: Northwestern University, Evanston Illinois.
Lines: 551

Hi everyone!

I have received a few suggestions thus far.  Thanks a lot.  However, some
changes will not be made immediately (such as adding some variations) since
it will take too much time.  My plan is to post these games first, and
re-edit the comments and add variations in the future.  When *that* is
finished, I will probably submit these commented games to milton ftp site.

This is the 3rd game, and this game is dedicated to *ychen 6d*.  He has
been a good friend I made on IGS although we've never met.  I respect him
not just because he's one of the best players on the server (in fact, I
wasn't so happy when he beat me up :) but also, he is one of the nicest
person around.

If ychen 6d had the honor to play Jiang Zhujiu pro 9 dan's first game on
IGS, then I had the honor to play *his* first game on IGS. :-)

jzy NR ^_^

