Comment[Black wins by 14 1/2 zi.

Overview: W grabbed an early lead.  But in the battle at the upper left corner, W 59, a huge mistake, gave B the chance.  B thereafter played better and better, looking like a complete different player from the "first half."

Quite a few good moves in the game.  However, casual moves like B 68, B 86 and W 87 left some "spots on the jade."]
